percent in march the cpi figures for april will be released next 
week 
the april increase brought the overall wholesale price index to 
1069 this means that a selection of wholesale goods costing 100 
during a 1982 base period would have cost 10690 last month this 
index itself is not adjusted for seasonal variations as are other 
figures in the report 
